Params: {2: 'Kamui', 3: "Because you're wrong from the start, Camu! It's not only power that can protect yourself!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'My reliable companions will be there for me as well!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'But, I must admit, I was wrong too.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "I am weak. Far weaker than you. And it's because of you that I can control Tenebrion and repel the viral corruption.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "It's with your help that I managed to get this far.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: 'Yet one body can never have two consciousnesses within it.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'I know, but neither of us has to disappear.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Because, you are me, and I am you. We're both Kamui.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: '...How long did it take you? You finally understood the crux of the problem...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: 'You have shown me very well that you have the mettle to fulfill your promise of protecting everything.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Oh, Bianca, can you stop pointing that thing at my head? It's dangerous!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "I only managed to make contact with you with Commandant's guidance and Liv's assistance.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Well, I don't understand the details, but I'm still thankful all the same. It's thanks to you all that I've managed to return.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Let's leave the talk for later. We need to extract from here now.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'If we stay for too long, we might give the Ascendants a chance.', 4: '2'}
